RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM (SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, B.FIELD_DESC AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE A, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.FIELD_NAME AND B.MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND A.RATE_CODE_USAGE = B.FIELD_TYPE UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, A.RATE_DESCR AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE A, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND B.CCY_CODE = ? AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE UNION SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC, AUTH_STAT, RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE = 'S') WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY RATE_CODE

SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE WHERE BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND TYPE = NVL(?,TYPE) ORDER BY RATE_CODE
SELECT RATE_CODE,RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE='P' AND RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' ORDER BY RATE_CODE
select customer_no, customer_name1 from oltms_customer where once_auth='Y'

SELECT SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO, COUNTERPARTY, CUSTOMER_NAME1, CURRENCY, PRODUCT_CODE, MODULE, BRANCH, SSI_MNEMONIC, PAY_AC_BRANCH, PAY_ACCOUNT, PAY_ACCOUNT_CCY, RECV_AC_BRANCH, RECV_ACCOUNT, RECV_ACCOUNT_CCY, ACC_WITH_INSTN1, BENEF_INSTITUTION1, ULT_BENEFICIARY1 FROM OLTMS_INSTR A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE COUNTERPARTY = ? AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' and A.record_stat = 'O' AND B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY AND branch in (GLOBAL.current_branch,'ALL') and module in ('LB','LP','AL') and currency in (?)
